headline: Generac price target lowered to $202 from $210 at Guggenheim
summary: Guggenheim lowered the firm’s price target on Generac (GNRC) to $202 from $210 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares. The firm made adjustments to its model to reflect potential weakness in the home standby generator market resulting from this year’s relatively calm weather. headline: How Recent Developments Are Shaping the Generac Story According to Wall Street Analysts
summary: Generac Holdings' consensus analyst price target has seen a slight decrease, moving from $206.81 to $203.88. This modest shift reflects Wall Street’s tempered optimism, as experts weigh the company’s strong execution in key market segments alongside concerns about near-term demand pressures.
